N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1220.17 - Permission required to post or distribute commercial signs, advertisements, etc

State Regulations

No person shall post, distribute or display commercial
signs, advertisements, circulars or printed or written material within the
terminal without permission. Notes
